name: Styro Art
overview:
StyroArt recognises the value of Visual Impact in promoting your product or service.

Established in 1987, StyroArt has been producing Visual Merchandise for some of the world’s leading global companies. StyroArt’s experience not only ensures your products stand out but they have that wow factor that makes them great.

To meet your needs we offer the latest in innovative products to ensure the first impression is a positive experience.
